OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start with some
OL,6,Fpatchy rain or drizzle, especially
OL,7,Fover higher ground. Some brighter
OL,8,Fspells developing to the north of high
OL,9,Fground during the afternoon, whereas
OL,10,Felsewhere remaining rather cloudy with
OL,11,Fsome further rain. Winds strengthening
OL,12,Flater.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA band of heavy rain and
OL,15,Fstrong winds will move eastwards this
OL,16,Fevening. Rain clearing during the
OL,17,Fearly hours allowing some clearer
OL,18,Fspells and a few showers to follow.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
