OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA brighter day on Wednesday
OL,6,Fwith a mix of cloud and sunny spells.
OL,7,FA few showers possible, especially
OL,8,Fnear north and west facing coasts.
OL,9,FWinds easing with temperatures near
OL,10,Fnormal.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FWet
OL,13,Fand windy on Thursday with gales
OL,14,Fpossible for a time. Colder on Friday
OL,15,Fwith blustery showers, occasionally
OL,16,Fwintry, especially in the north. Drier
OL,17,Fand less cold on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
